                           

                    M.W.B.  PRESENTS ........

                    D A M O C L E S   SOLUTION!!
                    ****************************


FIRSTLY,DO AS THE PRESIDENT SAYS,
AND GO TO THE ROOM AT THE END OF THE CORIDOR ON THE SECOND FLOOR.
ANSWER "OK" TO THE QUESTION,
AND GO BACK DOWN TO THE BASEMENT.
GET THE KEY,AND GO TO YOUR SHIP.
FLY TO 09-02 CAPITAL CITY, AND YOU WILL FIND A LIFT.
GO TO THE BASEMENT AND PICK UP THE ANTIGRAV.
RETURN TO YOUR SHIP AND FLY TO 12-14 CAPITAL CITY.
PICK UP THE A TO Z COMPUTER.
SWITCH IT ON.
(IT WILL CONSTANTLY TELL YOU YOUR LOCATION!)
FLY TO KEY WEST,AND THEN TO LOCATION 07-07.
ENTER THE BUILDING AND GO DOWN TO THE BASEMENT.
HERE YOU WILL FIND ANOTHER ANTIGRAV.
COLLECT IT,AND GO TO THE TRADING POST.
SELL ONE OF THE ANTIGRAVS.
(THE OTHER WILL ALLOW YOU TO PICK UP SPACECRAFT,CARS ETC)
FROM HERE ,GO TO SNOW ISLAND.
LOCATION 03-00.
HERE YOU SHOULD COLLECT THE CUPBOARD.
(WHICH IS ACTUALL A TRIGGER FOR THE NOVABOMB)
GO ON TO BARE ISLAND.
LOCATION 06-02.
MAKE SURE YOU TAKE YOUR SHIP INTO THE BUILDING WITH YOU!
DROP THE CUPBOARD ON THE GROUND FLOOR.
HERE THERE ARE TELEPORTERS MARKED 0-9.
GO TO "0".
WHERE THE COMPUTER WILL INFORM YOU'RE IN THE PROFESSOR'S NEW HOUSE. 
IN ONE OF THE ROOMS,YOU WILLFIND A SIDEBOARD.
(ANOTHER TRIGGER)
TAKE THIS BACK TO TELEPORTER 1.
LEAVE IT THERE.
GO THROUGH THE TELEPORTERS UNTILL THE COMPUTER TELLS YOU
THAT YOU'RE IN THE VESTA PARLIAMENT.
TAKE A LIFT TO THE TOP FLOOR,
WHERE YOU'LL FIND A BRIEFCASE.
(THIS ALLOWS YOU TO CARRY MORE OBJECTS)
GO BACK TO THE BASEMENT AND USE TELEPORTER 6.
LEAVE THE BUILDING.
GO BACK TO YOUR SHIP.
FLY TO 05-06.
BUY THE HI-FI.
(THE NEXT TRIGGER)
LEAVE THE ISLAND.
FLY TO 09-02 UR CITY.
FROM HERE ,ENTER THE BUILDING AND GO TO THE BASEMENT.
IGNORE THE PIANO.
NOTE:MWB DID ALL THE TYPING!
GO AROUND TO THE BACK OF THE  LIFT.
HERE YOU'LL FIND THE NOVABOMB.
NOW FLY BACK TO 08-08.
CHALDEA METROPOLIS.
(USE THE COMPUTER TO FIND IT)
FROM HERE ,TAKE THE BOMB AND THE TRIGGERS BACK TO TELEPORTER 1.
SET ALL TRIGGERS TO "ON"!
USE THE TELEPORTERS AND GO TO METIS.
ON ARRIVAL,THE A TO Z WILL TELL YOU'RE IN DOOBURY'S SOLICITORS.
DON'TGO TO FLOOR 8,OR YOU'LL BE SUED AND LOOSE ALL YOUR MONEY.
LEAVE THE BUILDING AND HEAD DOWN THE ROAD ON YOUR LEFT.
AT THE END OF THE ROAD IS A COURT.
ENTER.
WALK STRAIGHT ACROSS THE ROOM AND INTO THE WALL.
THE WALL WILL THEN OPEN,REVEALING THE LAST TRIGGER.
D O  N O T  T U R N  I T  O N!!!!!!!
LEAVE THE COURT  AND FLY INTO SPACE.
LAND ON DAMOCLES,AND DROP THE BOMB.
LEAVE DAMOCLES.
FLY AWAY.
(BE CAREFUL OF THE AMOUNT OF TIME)
WHEN YOU'RE FAR ENOUGH FROM THE COMET,ENGAGE THE LAST TRIGGER,
AND GOODBYE DAMOCLES!
SO THAT'S ALL FOR THE GAME!!!!



